              <p class="card-text mg-b-0"><b>Do third parties see and/or have access to information obtained by the Application?</b></p>
              <p class="card-text">Only aggregated, anonymized data is periodically transmitted to external services to help us improve the Application and our service. We will share your information with third parties only in the ways that are described in this privacy statement.We may disclose User Provided and Automatically Collected Information:<br>
