              <p class="card-text mg-b-0"><b>Security</b></p>
              <p class="card-text">We are concerned about safeguarding the confidentiality of your information. We provide physical, electronic, and procedural safeguards to protect information we process and maintain. For example, we limit access to this information to authorized employees and contractors who need to know that information in order to operate, develop or improve our Application. Please be aware that, although we endeavor provide reasonable security for information we process and maintain, no security system can prevent all potential security breaches.</p>

              <p class="card-text mg-b-0"><b>Changes</b></p>
